===== Template =====

This class is designed to work with templates. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:template:object#template|Template]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:create|template.create]]'' - creating new templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:delete|template.delete]]'' - deleting templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:get|template.get]]'' - retrieving templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:massadd|template.massadd]]'' - adding related objects to templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:massremove|template.massremove]]'' - removing related objects from templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:massupdate|template.massupdate]]'' - replacing or removing related objects from templates
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:template:update|template.update]]'' - updating templates